title: State v. Pamela Lanier – Episode 3 – Eliminate the Impossible
description:
May 7, 2018 / The Undisclosed team explores the two months between Dorian Lanier’s bulldozer accident and his death.

Episode scoring music by Animal Weapon. Additional scoring music by Blue Dot Sessions, Dr. Turtle, Kei Engel and Nctrnm.

This episode was sponsored by Boll & Branch.

www.BollandBranch.com use promo code Undisclosed.

#undisclosed #freepamlanier
